{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0005","text":"永遠造夢 也可以","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["夢想","可能性"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["永遠","造夢","可以"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,2,2,5,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["wing5","jyun5","zou6","mung6","jaa5","ho2","ji5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"永遠","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"造夢","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可以","pos":"AUX"}],"syntax_notes":"簡短的陳述句，強調即使在虛幻的夢境中，也覺得一切皆有可能。"},"source":{"title":"他有什麼好","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4141","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0006","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0006","text":"若可以不說一句他的事","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["逃避","自我欺騙"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不說","他的事"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,9,5,3,4,3,4,3,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","ho2","ji5","bat1","syut3","jat1","geoi3","taa1","dik1","si6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"可以","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"不說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一句","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"事","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以條件句開頭，表達為了避免談論「他」而產生的行為。"},"source":{"title":"他有什麼好","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4141","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0007","text":"便能自欺已跟你一對是不是","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["自我欺騙","懷疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["自欺","一對","是不是"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,0,2,3,5,3,5,3,4,2,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bin6","nang4","zi6","hei1","ji5","gan1","nei5","jat1","deoi3","si6","bat1","si6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"自欺","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"已","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一對","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是不是","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"描述透過逃避談論「他」來達到自我欺騙，並質疑自己是否真的與對方是一對。"},"source":{"title":"他有什麼好","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4141","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_NDE0MQ_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
